title="Jacob Lurie">Jacob Lurie</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:meta
name="external">https://kerodon.net</fr:meta></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Kerodon is an online textbook on categorical homotopy theory and related mathematics. It currently consists of a handful of chapters, but should grow (slowly) over time. It is modeled on the <fr:link
type="local"
href="stacks-project.xml"
addr="stacks-project"
title="The Stacks project">Stacks project</fr:link>, and is maintained by <fr:link
type="local"
href="jacoblurie.xml"
addr="jacoblurie"
title="Jacob Lurie">Jacob Lurie</fr:link>.</fr:p><fr:p>Its infrastructure uses <fr:link
type="local"
href="gerby.xml"
addr="gerby"
title="Gerby">Gerby</fr:link>, which is maintained by <fr:link
type="local"
href="pieterbelmans.xml"
addr="pieterbelmans"
title="Pieter Belmans">Pieter Belmans</fr:link>. The design was created by Opus Design.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
